    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2298460/extras/6e14a810b49a83eb53309b9b4c1db10a.avif?t=1684566396\" width=600 height=130 /></span><br><br>Strawb is a puzzle game that combines platformer and puzzle elements in a hand-drawn comic style. Your goal is to reach your friend by clever movement and destruction of blocks.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2298460/extras/3dc608b1a93ab6f24195c72ce415feee.poster.avif?t=1684566396\" width=600 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2298460/extras/3dc608b1a93ab6f24195c72ce415feee.webm?t=1684566396\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2298460/extras/3dc608b1a93ab6f24195c72ce415feee.mp4?t=1684566396\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>.<br><br>Use interesting abilities and mechanics like teleportation or lasers to master all 50 unique puzzles.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2298460/extras/caa186101d87cdee2481d99063a8b9c4.poster.avif?t=1684566396\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2298460/extras/caa186101d87cdee2481d99063a8b9c4.webm?t=1684566396\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2298460/extras/caa186101d87cdee2481d99063a8b9c4.mp4?t=1684566396\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2298460/extras/93695cf25f5f27812fca885cbb324007.avif?t=1684566396\" width=600 height=130 /></span><br><br>- 50 unique puzzles with increasing difficulty.<br>- Mechanics such as teleportation, lasers and moving entire rows of blocks.<br>- Hand-painted comic style graphics.<br>- Global best times for each level.<br>. Future new levels will be included.<br>- Brain training ;)<br><br>Will you solve the puzzles and catch your friend by cleverly combining all the mechanics?<br><strong>Try it out!</strong><br><br><u>About me</u><br>I am a solo indiedev working on game development during my free time as a hobby.<br>Enjoy Strawb ;)",
